IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User georgepar.91@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show muw/georgepar.91@gmail.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail
Expunge Both
Far  :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile


